channel.title: Still having problems w/ Moparscape and Fedora Core 6
channel.description: Ok, yesterday I posted that I could not get MoparScape to run in fedora core 6 Linux. Since then, I have installed JDK 6, and now the program will start, but freeze when the red bar says "Starting" and the bottom status area says "Loading Objects". What is wrong? Can some one please help me?
